OL,3,CMinister quells conscription rumours
OL,4,Cfollowing suggestion of 'citizen army'
OL,6,FModels of conscription existed for two
OL,7,Fperiods in the UK - during and after
OL,8,Fthe First and Second World Wars - but
OL,9,Fcompulsory military service has not
OL,10,Fbeen in force since 1960.JBut in
OL,11,Faftermath of Russia's ongoing invasion
OL,12,Fof Ukraine, Western attention has
OL,13,Fturned to the readiness of Nato forces
OL,14,Fto defend its borders against any
OL,15,Fextension of Kremlin aggression.
