OL,3,CMinister quells conscription rumours
OL,4,Cfollowing suggestion of 'citizen army'
OL,6,FDefence Secretary Grant Shapps, who
OL,7,Fhas previously backed defence spending
OL,8,Frising to 3% of gross domestic product
OL,9,F- a measure of the size of the economy
OL,10,F- last week said it was currently
OL,11,Fbelow the target of 2.5%.
OL,13,FThe Conservative defence minister said
OL,14,FSir Patrick had raised a "separate but
OL,15,Fequally necessary debate" about how
OL,16,Fthe first wave of defenders can be
OL,17,Fbolstered in the event of a war.
OL,19,F"We have long had plans for
OL,20,Fremobilising service leavers and
OL,21,Fmobilising volunteers," he continued.
